text: My name is Nguyễn Hữu Nghĩa (Leo Nguyen).
I started knowing programming when I was in high school with my first language being pascal.
From there, I started liking it and set a goal to go to university and study information technology.
In 2016, I passed the university entrance exam and started attending the University of Science and Technology of Ho Chi Minh City.
Learning to improve foundational knowledge and soft skills,...
After 4 years of university I graduated and started looking for job opportunities for myself.
Currently, I'm a full-time software engineer and part-time freelancer
If you need to make a software or a website. I am very pleased to cooperate with you!
